{"tid":950055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大與廣州簽協議建香港科技大學(廣州)","createTime":"2018-12-21T08:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T10:35:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6d59c8c9f4a29af92501b1d76568fbdd49a026","tid":950055,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"科技大學與廣州市人民政府和廣州大學簽署協議，合作籌建香港科技大學(廣州)。科大表示，港科大(廣州)位於廣州市南沙區慶盛現代高端服務區，佔地1.13平方公里。廣州市政府同意承擔新校所有建設費用，並將參照香港教資會資助模式，承擔新校未來基本營運經費；科大負責新校的教學質量與相關政策，確保新校與科大具同等質量和水平。新校將以英文為基本語言，首階段先招收研究生，計劃將在校研究生逐步增至4000人。<br />\n<br />\n科大校董會主席廖長城感謝穗港政府支持計劃，希望將科大的辦學經驗和理念帶到廣州，與科大位於南沙的霍英東研究院及深圳研究院，共同為大灣區培育具創新能力的國際化高端人才。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1050072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1050072&d=KMFAk3JdVptrirVU0BTG%2B%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=c1e569a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1050072</a>"},{"pid":"7edf2531d78623f4b110e41b305b6741b3255d3b","tid":950055,"uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"中文大學（深圳）對  科技大學（廣州）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46936d50a02e03674980f438f41f1255d9b5aa19","tid":950055,"uid":87069,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"廣州科技大學(香港) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60eeb607e8567b40cb46e54071d76019c2ce181","tid":950055,"uid":201091,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:37:50.000Z","msg":"科大淪陷"},{"pid":"91e3addddd329e10d2c4c0393fc2a7f156b09d1d","tid":950055,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a60eeb607e8567b40cb46e54071d76019c2ce181","tid":950055,"uid":201091,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:37:50.000Z","msg"